				<textElement textAlignment="Center" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="14" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[<font size='4' color='#004280'><b>REPORT</b></font><br><font size='2' color='#004280'>SELF-ASSESSMENT SURVEY<br><font size='1' color='#004280'>Frozen Tissue - Part 2: Isolated Proteins (ISO Version 1)</font>]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
	</pageHeader>
	<detail>
		<band height="25" splitType="Prevent">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="25" y="0" width="272" height="25" uuid="be8a5def-a130-4dbe-9390-072fb210b9e9"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Bold.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Record ID]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<textField isStretchWithOverflow="true">
				<reportElement x="322" y="0" width="222" height="25" uuid="5c6d2924-aaee-420b-89ac-02491b4c2775"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Right" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Bold.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<textFieldExpression><![CDATA[$F{record_id}+"<br>"]]></textFieldExpression>
			</textField>
		</band>
		<band height="90">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="90" uuid="6d1b4af7-aea7-45f4-8164-1f59207f9f92"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Molecule profiles can change during primary sample collection, which is why transport, storage and processing may influence research results. Standardising the entire process from sample collection to the selection of appropriate analysis methods is therefore crucial. ]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="120">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="120" uuid="cd69c46a-2cdf-40ab-aae3-47574121dff4"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[The International Organization for Standardization published a standard to determine influencing factors and provide recommendations for the handling, documentation and processing of  frozen tissue specimens intended for protein analysis (ISO 20184-2, Molecular in vitro diagnostic examinations - Specifications for pre-examination processes for frozen tissue - Part 2: Isolated proteins). For further details, please visit the <a href="https://www.iso.org/standard/69801.html" target="_blank">ISO website</a>.]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="60">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="60" uuid="20f9f089-82f0-4d3e-be02-bb3564b48162"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[This Self-Assessment Survey will help you to assess and improve your sample processing.]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="105">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="105" uuid="03fad33a-ba2a-470d-aab2-906137e4453f"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[The questions are colour-coded. <font color="#ec6607">Orange</font> criteria are '<font color="#ec6607">shall</font>' criteria, meeting them is required according to the standard.  <font color="#004280">Blue</font> criteria are '<font color="#004280">should</font>' criteria, meeting them is recommended according to the standard. Making true and accurate statements will help you get genuine feedback on your sample collection procedures and, as a result, improve certain processes in the future.]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="52">
